IntProperty1Hint: Determines the type of hoop this will be. 0 = orange, 1 = yellow, 2 = green, 3 = blue, 4 = light blue, 5+ = purple
IntProperty2Hint: Determines how far the hoop can launch you.
FloatProperty1Hint: Determines how long a hoop will hold you before releasing. Higher numbers mean a faster release, however 0 will never release. Below 0 will instantly release.
FloatProperty2Hint: Determines how far left or right a hoop will travel before launching. This is relative to the hoop's set rotation.
FloatProperty3Hint: Determines how far forward or back a hoop will travel before launching. This is relative to the hoop's set rotation.
FloatProperty4Hint: Determines how far up or down a hoop will travel before launching. This is relative to the hoop's set rotation.
